data.description: This adorable home is located in West-end Beaumont. This spacious home includes a first floor master bed and bath with attached sun room. Separate living and dining area. The second floor features a game room, bedroom, and bathroom. The garage includes a utility room, workshop, and unfinished possible garage apartment. This home need some TLC to get back into move-in-ready shape. It's in a great location just waiting for the right person to bring it back to life.
